@gaiyaa  @PPianAIC  -- You can go through this documentation for setting it up. 
https://docs.prylabs.network/docs/install/install-with-script
There's a good checklist here, explaining how to run a node after the merge on PoS: https://launchpad.ethereum.org/en/merge-readiness/
